    <div class="container">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p>Effective Date: 15/01/2025</p>
        
        <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p><strong>Automatically Collected Data:</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li>Device Information: Device model, operating system, and unique device identifiers.</li>
            <li>Gameplay Data: Level progress, in-game actions (e.g., where the player died, time spent on a level), and game preferences.</li>
            <li>Country: Automatically detected based on your connection.</li>
            <li>Crash Reports: Data on crashes and errors for improving performance.</li>
        </ul>
        <p><strong>Data from Third-Party Services:</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li>Unity Analytics: For tracking in-game behavior and performance.</li>
            <li>Unity Ads: (planned) For displaying in-game advertisements.</li>
            <li>Unity Cloud Save: For storing game settings and progress (graphics, language preferences).</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>To improve gameplay experience and balance game mechanics.</li>
            <li>To analyze user behavior for game development.</li>
            <li>To provide personalized content and updates.</li>
            <li>To deliver and manage in-game advertisements (when implemented).</li>
            <li>To store and synchronize game progress across devices.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. Sharing Your Information</h2>
        <p>We do not share your personal data with third parties except:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>With Unity Technologies (Unity Analytics, Ads, and Cloud Save services).</li>
            <li>When required by law.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>4. Data Security</h2>
        <p>We implement appropriate security measures to protect your data. However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure.</p>

        <h2>5. Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>Our Game is not directed to children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal data from children.</p>

        <h2>6. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us via our official Twitter page: <a href="#">https://x.com/Ulv_Bogdan</a></p>
